  <brief_title>Investigation of Radiofrequency Device for Treatment of Wrinkles and Rhytides</brief_title>
  <official_title>Radiofrequency Magnetic Induction Device for Use in Dermatologic Procedures for the Non-Invasive Treatment of Wrinkles and Rhytides</official_title>
