  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot research study is to collect information on the safety and
      effectiveness of an experimental device intended to be used to improve the appearance of the
      skin by reducing the visibility of wrinkles and by reducing the looseness of skin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
